PrecisAmendments to the PENSION BENEFITS STANDARDS REGULATIONS, 1985, four of which either exempt or apply all or part of the Act to certain pension plans, benefits and contributors, while the others establish funding requirements for existing plans that were not subject to the Act prior to January 1, 1987, or change the minimum death benefit payable to a surviving spouse under a deferred annuity contract.

precis:
Amendments to the PENSION BENEFITS STANDARDS REGULATIONS, 1985, four of
which either exempt or apply all or part of the Act to certain pension
plans, benefits and contributors, while the others establish funding
requirements for existing plans that were not subject to the Act prior to
January 1, 1987, or change the minimum death benefit payable to a surviving
spouse under a deferred annuity contract.
